To get Ethnio's version of rspec_autotest running...

 * Installation...
   * Install Growl and growlnotify (http://growl.info)
   * Install zentest and diff-lcs gems:
     $ sudo gem install zentest
     $ sudo gem install diff-lcs

 * Running...
   $ rake spec:autotest    # from the project root

this starts the monitor.

Every save will run the tests.